  });
}) (Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor(Image.prototype, "src"));

### What is expected?
图片的加载内容是转码后的base64
exp: <div style="url(xxxx.jpg)" />   => <div style="url(base64)" />

### What is actually happening?
1. async set function被执行两次；
2. 并不能用base64替代转码前的URL，图片加载报错；

---
